---
title: "_onAuctionEnd (BaseAuction + GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_gpv2: GPV2CompatibleAuction override
    q_check_gpv2 --> q_revoke_approval: revoke CowSwap vault relayer allowance
    q_revoke_approval --> q_check_feeagg: forceApprove(vaultRelayer, 0)
    q_check_feeagg --> q_return_asset: hasFeeAggregator == true
    q_check_feeagg --> q_check_assetout_balance: hasFeeAggregator == false
    q_return_asset --> q_check_asset_balance: check remaining asset balance
    q_check_asset_balance --> q_transfer_back: assetBalance > 0
    q_check_asset_balance --> q_check_assetout_balance: assetBalance == 0
    q_transfer_back --> q_check_assetout_balance: safeTransfer(feeAggregator, assetBalance)
    q_check_assetout_balance --> q_transfer_assetout: assetOutBalance > 0
    q_check_assetout_balance --> [*]: assetOutBalance == 0
    q_transfer_assetout --> [*]: safeTransfer(assetOutReceiver, assetOutBalance)

    note right of q_return_asset
        INV-001: Remaining unsold assets are returned to feeAggregator
        INV-002: Accumulated assetOut (settlement) is forwarded to assetOutReceiver
        INV-003: CowSwap vault relayer approval is revoked on auction end
    end note
